reviews.review_text:
overlooked show! Initially only streamed to listen to Morning Dew, but it was so good that I ended up listening to the entire show!

IMHO any Dew is a good Dew; it used to be that if they played Morning Dew, it was a great show, regardless of what the rest of the show was like. Don't get me wrong--this is not an earthshattering Dew my any stretch of the imagination--though I'm sure with a little extra chemical assistance many in attendance that night had seemingly supernatural experiences during Dew.

Anyway, nice show--sure wish somebody would post a board of this show!
